1
00:00:09,330 --> 00:00:10,390
Greetings, Madam.

2
00:00:12,630 --> 00:00:13,260
Rise.

3
00:00:14,360 --> 00:00:16,660
I am no longer the Minister's wife.

4
00:00:16,860 --> 00:00:18,990
There is no need for such formalities.

5
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:21,160
The Minister's Manor has been very kind to me.

6
00:00:21,160 --> 00:00:23,200
If it weren't for the Minister's Manor's cultivation back then,

7
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:25,160
teaching me to read, write, and practice martial arts,

8
00:00:25,160 --> 00:00:26,430
even if I encountered opportunities,

9
00:00:26,430 --> 00:00:28,360
I wouldn't have the ability to reach where I am today.

10
00:00:28,360 --> 00:00:30,160
I am now the General of Weibei.

11
00:00:30,160 --> 00:00:32,259
If I cannot take good care of my former benefactors,

12
00:00:32,259 --> 00:00:34,330
I, Lu Jingxing, would be living in vain.

13
00:00:34,330 --> 00:00:37,160
This man is quite eloquent now.

14
00:00:37,360 --> 00:00:38,700
He is so good with words,

15
00:00:38,830 --> 00:00:41,090
no wonder he has won His Majesty's favor.

16
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:47,000
These are the sword and dagger bestowed by His Majesty.

17
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:48,600
I am giving them to you today.

18
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:50,660
If you encounter a crisis like today's again,

19
00:00:50,660 --> 00:00:52,000
do you dare to draw your blades

20
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:53,000
to protect yourselves

21
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:54,400
and protect your sister?

22
00:00:55,500 --> 00:00:56,660
We dare.

23
00:00:56,860 --> 00:00:58,060
Thank you, General of Weibei.

24
00:00:58,060 --> 00:00:58,660
You're wrong.

25
00:00:58,660 --> 00:01:01,600
Now we should call him brother-in-law.

26
00:01:04,530 --> 00:01:05,700
Here, they are all for you.

27
00:01:05,700 --> 00:01:07,430
Play with them, little sister.

28
00:01:07,660 --> 00:01:08,700
Whatever my little sister likes,

29
00:01:08,700 --> 00:01:10,400
your brother-in-law will bring you mountains of gold and silver.

30
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:12,400
Just wait for your brother-in-law.

31
00:01:17,600 --> 00:01:19,900
Let's have a daughter in the future, okay?

32
00:01:19,900 --> 00:01:20,860
A daughter is good.

33
00:01:20,860 --> 00:01:23,030
A daughter is smart, clever, and eloquent.

34
00:01:23,030 --> 00:01:24,160
Be serious.

35
00:01:24,500 --> 00:01:25,560
Making such a scene tonight,

36
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:27,260
you'll have a tough battle to fight tomorrow.

37
00:01:27,260 --> 00:01:29,300
Grand Tutor Wei will definitely impeach you at the morning court.

38
00:01:29,300 --> 00:01:30,960
How do you plan to deal with it?

39
00:01:31,230 --> 00:01:32,360
What's there to deal with?

40
00:01:32,360 --> 00:01:33,430
What can he do to me?

41
00:01:33,830 --> 00:01:35,560
It's just lip service.

42
00:01:35,960 --> 00:01:37,229
I'm not afraid.

43
00:01:37,229 --> 00:01:38,500
It's true that you have outstanding military achievements.

44
00:01:38,500 --> 00:01:40,130
But the lip service in the court

45
00:01:40,130 --> 00:01:41,460
is sometimes more intense than the battlefield.

46
00:01:41,460 --> 00:01:42,660
It kills invisibly.

47
00:01:42,960 --> 00:01:44,000
A slight carelessness

48
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:45,960
will result in losing everything.

49
00:01:46,660 --> 00:01:47,520
Remember this.

50
00:01:47,759 --> 00:01:49,759
Grand Tutor Wei is good at quoting classics.

51
00:01:49,759 --> 00:01:52,400
You are not good at dealing with those pedantic words.

52
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,200
Then,

53
00:01:53,229 --> 00:01:55,430
drag him into the rhetoric you are good at,

54
00:01:55,430 --> 00:01:57,100
and leave him no room to perform.

55
00:01:57,100 --> 00:01:57,930
I understand.

56
00:01:58,300 --> 00:02:00,030
I'll listen to the strategist.

57
00:02:11,600 --> 00:02:12,660
Your Majesty,

58
00:02:12,660 --> 00:02:13,930
the General of Weibei, Lu Jingxing,

59
00:02:13,930 --> 00:02:16,260
acted recklessly in my Grand Tutor's Manor.

60
00:02:16,260 --> 00:02:17,829
He forced his way into the inner courtyard,

61
00:02:17,829 --> 00:02:19,000
ordered his men to open the manor gates,

62
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:20,160
pushed down the courtyard walls,

63
00:02:20,160 --> 00:02:22,560
and let the commoners watch my family members.

64
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:24,700
This caused my wife and daughter to be humiliated,

65
00:02:24,700 --> 00:02:27,230
and the Grand Tutor's Manor lost all its face.

66
00:02:27,230 --> 00:02:30,700
For such an act of ignoring the law and humiliating a court official,

67
00:02:30,700 --> 00:02:33,030
I beg Your Majesty to bring justice for me.

68
00:02:36,700 --> 00:02:37,930
General of Weibei,

69
00:02:38,300 --> 00:02:40,560
is what the Grand Tutor said true?

70
00:02:42,829 --> 00:02:43,630
Your Majesty.

71
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:44,500
I don't understand.

72
00:02:44,500 --> 00:02:46,900
What nonsense is Grand Tutor Wei babbling about?

73
00:02:46,900 --> 00:02:47,500
How vulgar.

74
00:02:47,500 --> 00:02:48,500
This is outrageous.

75
00:02:48,500 --> 00:02:49,500
Lu Jingxing,

76
00:02:49,500 --> 00:02:51,860
how dare you speak such filth in the grand hall?

77
00:02:51,860 --> 00:02:53,329
You have no respect for His Majesty!

78
00:02:53,329 --> 00:02:55,530
General Weibei's words are a bit rough,

79
00:02:55,730 --> 00:02:56,900
but I know him.

80
00:02:57,060 --> 00:02:58,730
He has always been straightforward.

81
00:02:58,730 --> 00:03:00,230
Your Majesty understands me best.

82
00:03:00,230 --> 00:03:03,060
Your Majesty, it was Grand Tutor Wei who summoned me yesterday.

83
00:03:03,060 --> 00:03:04,230
My soldiers

84
00:03:04,260 --> 00:03:06,560
and the servants in his mansion can all testify to that.

85
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:07,460
When I arrived,

86
00:03:07,460 --> 00:03:08,960
I saw the Grand Tutor and his wife

87
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:10,200
hugging

88
00:03:10,200 --> 00:03:11,260
and making out in the courtyard.

89
00:03:11,260 --> 00:03:13,800
I thought they were putting on a show specifically for me.

90
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,460
Thinking that a joy shared is a joy doubled,

91
00:03:15,460 --> 00:03:16,660
I had the main gates opened

92
00:03:16,660 --> 00:03:18,800
so everyone could witness their deep affection.

93
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:20,530
Yet how come he is now in front of Your Majesty,

94
00:03:20,530 --> 00:03:22,000
shifting the blame onto me?

95
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:24,000
He is clearly framing me on purpose.

96
00:03:24,260 --> 00:03:26,460
How did this brute become so crafty today?

97
00:03:26,460 --> 00:03:27,829
He speaks clearly,

98
00:03:27,829 --> 00:03:28,530
avoids the main points,

99
00:03:28,530 --> 00:03:29,660
and shifts the blame.

100
00:03:29,660 --> 00:03:31,700
Someone smart must be guiding him from behind.

101
00:03:31,700 --> 00:03:32,800
Nonsense!

102
00:03:32,860 --> 00:03:35,260
You clearly set this up to frame us.

103
00:03:35,260 --> 00:03:36,800
Frame you, my ass!

104
00:03:37,829 --> 00:03:38,960
His Majesty granted the marriage.

105
00:03:38,960 --> 00:03:40,060
I pinched my nose and agreed

106
00:03:40,060 --> 00:03:41,230
to marry your daughter.

107
00:03:41,230 --> 00:03:42,430
And what did you do?

108
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:43,530
You called me over

109
00:03:43,530 --> 00:03:44,600
to intentionally show me your daughter

110
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:45,800
forcing herself on a stable boy.

111
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,530
For the daughter of the Wei family to do such a scandalous thing,

112
00:03:47,530 --> 00:03:50,190
Grand Tutor Wei's upbringing is simply absurd.

113
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,800
Grand Tutor Wei,

114
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:57,400
is what General Lu said true?

115
00:03:57,730 --> 00:04:00,260
Your Majesty, there is a hidden truth to this matter.

116
00:04:00,260 --> 00:04:03,320
My daughter was framed into being with that stable boy.

117
00:04:08,100 --> 00:04:09,360
You lying old fool!

118
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:10,660
You are clearly humiliating me

119
00:04:10,660 --> 00:04:12,390
to slap His Majesty in the face.

120
00:04:14,430 --> 00:04:16,660
Even if I lose my general title today,

121
00:04:16,660 --> 00:04:18,860
I will vent this anger for Your Majesty!

122
00:04:25,500 --> 00:04:27,330
Grand Tutor Wei is the head of the civil officials.

123
00:04:27,330 --> 00:04:29,430
In the court, all eyes are on him.

124
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:31,200
And you just beat him up?

125
00:04:31,730 --> 00:04:33,659
How do you expect me to clean up this mess for you?

126
00:04:33,659 --> 00:04:36,120
I was wrong, but I really couldn't hold back.

127
00:04:36,130 --> 00:04:37,530
When I ascended the throne three years ago,

128
00:04:37,530 --> 00:04:39,159
Grand Tutor Wei made great contributions.

129
00:04:39,159 --> 00:04:40,600
I asked you to marry into the Wei family

130
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:41,860
to balance the civil and military officials

131
00:04:41,860 --> 00:04:43,260
and stabilize the court.

132
00:04:43,659 --> 00:04:45,920
Who knew his daughter would be so absurd?

133
00:04:46,159 --> 00:04:47,760
You truly have been wronged.

134
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:48,800
I am not wronged.

135
00:04:49,530 --> 00:04:50,400
For Your Majesty,

136
00:04:50,400 --> 00:04:52,060
I am willing to be a cuckold

137
00:04:52,060 --> 00:04:56,120
and go to the Grand Tutor's mansion to present the betrothal gifts today.

138
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:59,659
What do you mean 'be a cuckold for me'?

139
00:05:00,060 --> 00:05:02,900
Grand Tutor Wei's daughter is shallow, flamboyant, vicious, and pretentious.

140
00:05:02,900 --> 00:05:04,730
Whenever I see her, I want to draw my sword.

141
00:05:04,730 --> 00:05:06,260
Grand Tutor Wei is a cunning old fox.

142
00:05:06,260 --> 00:05:07,900
Whenever I see him, I want to punch him.

143
00:05:07,900 --> 00:05:09,930
But I know Your Majesty needs this marriage,

144
00:05:09,930 --> 00:05:12,460
so I am willing to sacrifice my own happiness.

145
00:05:12,500 --> 00:05:14,860
You are just too straightforward.

146
00:05:15,330 --> 00:05:17,660
You say whatever is on your mind.

147
00:05:17,860 --> 00:05:19,300
I am not afraid of offending people.

148
00:05:19,300 --> 00:05:21,300
I only need to be loyal to the most important person

149
00:05:21,300 --> 00:05:22,100
in my heart.

150
00:05:23,330 --> 00:05:24,390
You are loyal to me.

151
00:05:24,500 --> 00:05:26,100
I won't let you suffer any loss.

152
00:05:26,100 --> 00:05:28,860
Feel free to mention any requests you have for this marriage.

153
00:05:28,860 --> 00:05:30,260
If Grand Tutor Wei makes things difficult for you again,

154
00:05:30,260 --> 00:05:31,390
I will not spare him.

155
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:33,960
Grand Tutor Wei previously sent a pre-wedding maid,

156
00:05:33,960 --> 00:05:35,200
and she slept with me for three days.

157
00:05:35,200 --> 00:05:36,100
I like her.

158
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:39,430
Grand Tutor Wei is using her family's deeds to control me.

159
00:05:39,430 --> 00:05:41,700
Your Majesty, could you grant that family to me?

160
00:05:41,700 --> 00:05:42,960
How is that difficult?

161
00:05:43,159 --> 00:05:43,960
Granted.

162
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:46,560
Alright, go send the betrothal gifts.

163
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:47,430
Okay.

164
00:05:47,430 --> 00:05:49,760
My young lady truly foresaw everything.

165
00:05:49,930 --> 00:05:51,800
Just by saying the few words she taught me,

166
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:53,659
His Majesty agreed very readily.

167
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:56,900
I just granted him a few servants,

168
00:05:56,900 --> 00:05:58,200
and he's so happy.

169
00:05:58,260 --> 00:06:00,260
He really is a straightforward guy,

170
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:02,500
and truly my loyal subject.

171
00:06:09,030 --> 00:06:11,200
That Lu Jingxing is simply lawless.

172
00:06:11,460 --> 00:06:13,260
Beating someone openly in the court.

173
00:06:13,260 --> 00:06:14,660
Does he have any regard for the law

174
00:06:14,660 --> 00:06:15,430
or His Majesty?

175
00:06:15,430 --> 00:06:18,500
I used to think he was just a brawny warrior,

176
00:06:18,930 --> 00:06:21,730
but I didn't expect him to learn to play tricks now.

177
00:06:22,530 --> 00:06:23,530
It's all your fault!

178
00:06:23,530 --> 00:06:25,160
You suffered a double loss,

179
00:06:25,300 --> 00:06:27,130
causing me to lose all my face in the court.

180
00:06:27,130 --> 00:06:28,430
Why don't you just die?

181
00:06:28,530 --> 00:06:31,400
Master, I was also framed.

182
00:06:31,400 --> 00:06:32,560
Father, please don't hit Mother.

183
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:35,060
And you, you've completely disgraced the Wei family.

184
00:06:35,060 --> 00:06:36,260
Go to hell, all of you!

185
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:39,060
Go to hell!

186
00:06:40,659 --> 00:06:43,120
Useless trash, making a fool of yourselves!

187
00:06:51,830 --> 00:06:55,430
Shen Luyi is the cause of all this.

188
00:06:55,630 --> 00:06:57,060
How dare she scheme against us.

189
00:06:57,060 --> 00:06:58,600
I will make her pay back a hundredfold.

190
00:06:58,600 --> 00:06:59,659
Men!

191
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:03,560
Go catch Shen Luyi immediately,

192
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:04,900
bring her to my room.

193
00:07:04,900 --> 00:07:06,260
I will interrogate her myself.
